Starting line-ups for the Champions League final between Liverpool and Real Madrid at the Stade de France on Saturday (1900 GMT): Liverpool (4-3-3) Alisson Becker; Trent Alexander-Arnold, Ibrahima Konate, Virgil van Dijk, Andy Robertson; Fabinho, Thiago Alcantara, Jordan Henderson (capt); Mohamed Salah, Sadio Mane, Luis Diaz Coach: Jurgen Klopp (GER) Real Madrid (4-3-3) Thibaut Courtois; Dani Carvajal, Eder Militao, David Alaba, Ferland Mendy; Casemiro, Toni Kroos, Luka Modric; Fede Valverde, Karim Benzema (capt), Vinicius Junior Coach: Carlo Ancelotti (ITA) Referee: Clement Turpin (FRA) AFP